snippet.title: Monster Hunter 4 Ultimate - E3 2014 Trailer
snippet.description:
Monster Hunter 4 Ultimate is coming to the Nintendo 3DS in 2015!

Team up with up to 3 other hunters online to hunt epic monsters!

Monster Hunter 4 Ultimate will be available on the Nintendo 3DS on February 13th, 2015!
